discussiontools-notification-subscribed-:
{{optional}}
Notification compact header text for when there is a reply on a topic. Parameters:
* $1 - the formatted username of the user who replied to the topic
* $2 - the username for gender purposes
* $3 - excerpt of the reply.
{{Related|discussiontools-notification-header-flow}}

discussiontools-pagetitle-newtopic:
Shown as page title when starting a new topic on a talk page. Parameters:
* $1 - the name of the page the user is starting a new topic on. e.g. "Starting new topic on Talk:Main Page"
{{Related|discussiontools-pagetitle-reply}}

discussiontools-pagetitle-reply:
Shown as page title when composing a reply on a talk page. Parameters:
* $1 - the name of the page the user is replying on. e.g. "Replying on Talk:Main Page"
{{Related|discussiontools-pagetitle-newtopic}}

discussiontools-postedit-confirmation-pu:
{{gender}}
Success message shown after a user publishes a comment on a page. Parameters:
* $1 - the current user, for GENDER support

See also: {{msg-mw|postedit-confirmation-published}}

discussiontools-postedit-confirmation-to:
{{gender}}
Success message shown after a user adds a new topic on a page. Parameters:
* $1 - the current user, for GENDER support

See also: {{msg-mw|postedit-confirmation-published}}

